Lotus is the national flower of India and has often been called Sacred Lotus.

The fresh and gorgeous Jasmine flowers are the pride of India.

Sunflower is the most beautiful flower in India and is known for its fiery bloom.

Roses are widely used across the world as symbols of love, sympathy or sorrow.

Marigolds are plants that bear brightly colored blooms.

The lily is a genus of flowering plant.
